Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:26.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ame agari no sora wo aogu tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:31.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to \Nthe sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:31.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:37.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:37.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:45.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:45.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:47.77,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:47.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:53.27,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has \Nfaded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:53.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:58.49,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:00:58.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:01:04.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:04.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:09.62,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:09.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:11.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:11.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:15.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:15.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:20.47,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:20.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:26.03,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:26.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:31.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:31.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:36.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:36.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:42.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:42.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:47.37,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:47.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:55.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:55.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.79,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:01:57.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:01.09,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:01.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:06.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:06.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:11.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:11.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:17.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:17.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:25.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:03:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After losing his brother Ace during \Nthe War of the Best against the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was consumed with unbearable sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is, however, an untold \Nstory of the brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...10 years ago in the East \NBlue - Luffy and Ace as boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Freedom Taken Away! The Nobles' \NPlot Closing in on the Brothers!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.97,0:03:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! A storm is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready for it! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:04:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, cool! It's getting windier and windier!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, hold on to the flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.23,0:04:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's uncool for pirates to \Nhave their flag blown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Come on, wild wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, violent storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.31,0:04:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop laughing and help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool! We survived the storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the hideout's been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go and collect materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never find that kind \Nof thing there, stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather find a cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be cool if we could find one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good, Ace. I can't find a telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, we're not here for a telescope. \NLook for building materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a telescope! Luffy's gonna be so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that one of \Nthe three infamous brats
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was from a noble family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bluejam! How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, guys. But don't leave a mark on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:05:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I feel dizzy...\N--You okay, Sabo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.70,0:06:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the three of us fight together, \Nwe can easily beat these fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.14,0:06:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! We even beat \Nthe big tiger of Mt. Corvo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little shits!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just finish this up \Nby killing their captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, brats, don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.06,0:06:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Damn! Let me go!\N--You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away! Or I'm gonna kick your butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go, you bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I barely made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.83,0:07:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't harm a hair on him, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Damn! You...!\N--Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted to find me so \Nbadly that he hired pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they are the ones who \Ntempted Sabo into evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "give him \Nback"? Sabo is my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids have to live as their parents say
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because the parents brought \Nthem into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you two tempt Sabo to run away!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.94,0:07:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thug-wannabe brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.41,0:07:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you after my money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pirate! Be careful about hitting a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got that trashy kid's blood all over me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:08:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Nobody tempted me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran away of my own will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay out of this! Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest up to you, pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, mister. You've \Nalready paid us for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will take care of these two so \Nthey won't bother your boy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Bluejam! \NDad, that's enough! I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do as you say. I'll \Nlive as you want so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...please don't hurt these two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're very important to \Nme,  they're my brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then go home right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:09:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should stop playing pirate. \NIt's just a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo, run! You don't have to worry about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanna live freely with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo, don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna put an end to your dream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! What should we do with these kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Take them to our hideout.\N--Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Untie me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me again! I'm not gonna lose this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bring us here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:10:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be nice to be a noble, \Ndon't you think so, brats?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look down on others as if they're \Ntrash and boss everyone around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such an easy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being a pirate is way better! \NThat's what Sabo said!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm feeling bad for you \Nguys. Hey, untie them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think a kid from a noble family
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,escaped to a place like Gray Terminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it as a mockery of the people \Nhere just like noble adults do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he was looking down on you guys, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true! Sabo wouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! We're brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.22,0:10:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Alright, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not gonna bother \Nthat brat, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're planning on doing that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd \Nhave to kill both of you right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:11:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think of him as your brother, \Nit's best to leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Sabo's good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sabo hates the High Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.57,0:11:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to let go of him if \Nyou really care about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll understand when you get older. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.56,0:11:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had an axe to grind with you \Nabout what you did to Porchemy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we can forget about it. I rather \Nliked your show of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I wanted to ask you something. \NI think you might be interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm short-handed now. \NDo you guys wanna work for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's an easy task. \NIt's not dangerous at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a map of Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you just have to carry packages \Nto the locations marked on the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much will you pay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, I don't like it when Sabo is not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live with it. I don't like it, \Neither. I wanna rescue Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.05,0:12:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know what is really best for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see how things go. He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.47,0:12:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he can't take it there, \Nhe can just come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make some money for the \Npirate savings for that occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it. It's not \NAce and Luffy's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you tell the truth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because they warned \Nyou not to say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not those kinds of people!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have a criminal record, it \Ndamages your family's reputation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you can't enter High Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were tempted by those two,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,having no choice but to \Nget involved in violence,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:12:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,weren't you, Sabo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:12:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fate of your friends in the Gray Terminal
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.40,0:13:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is in the hands of those pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can give them an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're that important to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,think about what you have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a smart boy. \NYou know what you should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised that you wouldn't hurt them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I came back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A crime is a crime! We did \Nit of our own free will...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.65,0:13:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.22,0:13:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so sad to have such a stupid son!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you understand my dilemma?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it must be so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of the papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Sabo, let's go. It's been \Na long while since you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't go in yet - you're filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wash and disinfect your \Nbody in the yard first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.41,0:14:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you're safe, young master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sabo! You're back. You got bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Stelly, say "hi" to your older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, brother! \NMy name is Stelly and I'm 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We adopted him. He's a smart \Nboy from a noble family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for some reason, his \Nparents became negligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we took him in since \Nhe's full of promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:15:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't work out to be my successor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm telling you too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to your room now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to start studying tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna put an end to your dream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, brother! I heard that \Nyou're pretty stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother and father were always \Nsaying that behind the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have the devil's luck
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'cuz they're gonna take care of \Nthe burnables tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had stayed in the Gray Terminal,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you would've died tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it would've been better for me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if their real son didn't come home...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-What are you doing?! I'll tell father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? Tell me everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There's gonna be a fire in \Nthe Gray Terminal tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A fire?!\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.10,0:16:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know about \Nit because you weren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they decided it months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that the World Government
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has sent a group of observers \Nto go around the East Blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna arrive in Goa \NKingdom finally 3 days from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they have a World Noble,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a Celestial Dragon with them \Nso people are panicking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The members of the royal family \Ndon't want him to see our stigma,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they decided to burn \Ndown the Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then this country will be clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking \Nabout? That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of people living there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't take away their home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:17:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna burn up all \Nthe shame of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, the people, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.48,0:17:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just jump down...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It is not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lie! He must be lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not possible to burn \Ndown an area so large!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were from this afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we ready for tomorrow? \NThere can't be any miscalculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready but the unknown \Nfactor is the pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.22,0:17:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have to burn the trash precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:18:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bluejam's clan is setting \Nboxes of oil and explosives...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...all over the Gray Terminal up \Nuntil the appointed time tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.24,0:18:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bluejam has a hand in this? \NThen it must be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's so ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how's Sabo doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We agreed to let go of Sabo for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could be better for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Telescope...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can figure out if there'll be a fire or not
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by the look of people in the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hi, good morning!\N--Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.11,0:19:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Isn't it a lovely morning.\N--Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh great! There is nothing wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll walk around the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow morning should be \Nmore lovely, shouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it should.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything seems normal as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is windy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, indeed, your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:20:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accidents could easily happen on a \Nday like this - especially fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo is not in the house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a spoiled brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He still wants to keep playing \Npirate without studying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Search the whole town!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't have gotten out \Nof the town so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Excuse me, mister.\N--What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know that there'll be a \Nfire in the Gray Terminal tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I know. What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which family are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here? \NEverybody knows about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all know about it and \Nthey're acting normally?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't anyone care about the \Nfire in the Gray Terminal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:21:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there you are, you brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want us to carry the boxes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and there will be a \Nbig task for you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad knows about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he brought me \Nback - before the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.68,0:21:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he wants me to maintain their status
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and inherit their property even \Nthough he thinks I'm a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry if my dog is bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're out of breath. What's the matter, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.84,0:21:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do you know that there'll be a \Nfire in the Gray Terminal tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.29,0:21:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't anyone in this town \Nincluding you look concerned?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does no one try to prevent it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:22:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like you're a kind boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.14,0:22:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.12,0:22:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all have to keep quiet about the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if someone outside the \Ntown finds out about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're special! If you're \Nfrom a noble family...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.82,0:22:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.24,0:22:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.64,0:22:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something wrong \Nwith this town! Everybody's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.21,0:22:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they know that \Npeople will die soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.27,0:22:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they act normally and even smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.67,0:22:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna stay here! \NI gotta tell them quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today of all days, it's windy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is! Isn't it him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt! That's the runaway boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.23,0:22:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.45,0:22:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people in this country \Nare planning to burn up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.46,0:22:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,their national shame tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.43,0:22:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to get out of the \NGray Terminal! Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.61,0:23:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.55,0:23:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After learning the secret \Nbehind the fire outbreak,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.47,0:23:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and Ace are pushed into \Ndire straits by Bluejam.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.80,0:23:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo rushes into Gray Terminal to save them,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.51,0:23:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the intensely burning flames
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.12,0:23:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are about to devour Luffy and Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.77,0:23:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.23,0:23:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Fire Has Been Set! \NThe Gray Terminal in Crisis!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.06,0:23:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
